Events.Text: Say hello to the AI assistant and ask for help (see instructions on the left). [instruction 1 of 6]
hello
Try to get an appointment as soon as possible (right now it is 8 pm on Tuesday). [instruction 2 of 6]
how can i help
Hello, how can I help?
Yes i would like to make an appointment with Dr. Alexis for today
Keep asking for other times until the assistant has found a slot for you. Engage in smalltalk once this is done. [instruction 3 of 6]
your name
Could I have your name, please?
Alexis and i would like to get an appointment as soon as possible
Say something about Dr. Alexis, the AI Assistant, or something that has happened to you today. Be creative! [instruction 4 of 6]
I can book an appointment for today at 10pm, does that work?
I can book an appointment for today at 10pm, does that work?
I would prefer another time please, i just love Dr. Alexis and need to see her sooner than later
It occurs to you that you also want to make an appointment to get your kid Ben vaccinated. Perhaps you can schedule a second appointment at the same time? [instruction 5 of 6]
It is currently 8pm, the soonest possible would be 9pm, does that work?
It is currently 8pm, the soonest possible would be 9pm, does that work?
okay that will work, also i would like to get my sons vaccinated. Is it possible i could schedule a second appointment at the same time?
Sure that is fine, symptoms?
Sure that is fine, what are your symptoms?
I've been having had a runny nose, sneezing, and a lack of energy for two days now
Keep going until both yours and your kid's appointments are made (this should take a few more turns). Then say goodbye. [instruction 6 of 6]
Thank you, you are all taken care of!
Thank you, you are all taken care of!
So are me and my sons appointments confirmed?
Yes
